{"data":[{"id":563778197,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3e51319744d2c3d4b5a276b693ddc0d2","url_token":"qian-qu-zi-yu","name":"千曲子语","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d438b0948a93c1afdcd5b9587eb43e35_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d438b0948a93c1afdcd5b9587eb43e35_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3e51319744d2c3d4b5a276b693ddc0d2","user_type":"people","headline":"一个没脱离低级趣味的人","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":18,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563778197","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9f8f73671dfb16f920bcd2d141103278_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546275808,"updated_time":1546312238,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e反正我也是高中生，我觉得能证明证明哥猜的证明是错的，要是我错了也无所谓，新年快乐。\u003cbr\u003e问题我觉得就出在正数第八行（旧版本知乎翻不到写公式的东西所以纯文字了）\u003cbr\u003e“若对于任意一个n属于正整数，使得2n均属于'A，则-1不是质数”\u003cbr\u003e然后我们翻看此前的定义“如果把-1归到质数集合中”，因此是先假定了-1是质数，再推导出了上述命题，要证明-1不是质数。（此为错误一）\u003cbr\u003e然后我们在看命题本身\u003cbr\u003e2n属于A的条件是-1和2n+1都是质数，-1是质数（负质数，扩展定义暂且不说）是我们假定的条件，但是逆否命题里却只有-1为质数，而2n+1也应该是质数这一条件被忽略了。（错误二）\u003cbr\u003e如果补充上这一条件即\u003cbr\u003e“存在n属于正整数使得2n不属于A，则-1不为质数或2n+1不为质数。”\u003cbr\u003e至于2n+1为不为质数不重要，少了这么个条件，以下证明全错。\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fad7ff769f5cf80c1d7f2c0c1b181d93_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5f87c1957aaefa6554386828270d4b90_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fad7ff769f5cf80c1d7f2c0c1b181d93_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5f87c1957aaefa6554386828270d4b90_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fad7ff769f5cf80c1d7f2c0c1b181d93_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fad7ff769f5cf80c1d7f2c0c1b181d93_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e图好像显示不出来了我明天换个手机玩玩，总之抛砖引玉，希望是我错了，希望中国出了个数学鬼才。\u003cbr\u003e以上。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外评论里的链接大家可以看一下，我觉得说的很有道理（借机涨粉）\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"反正我也是高中生，我觉得能证明证明哥猜的证明是错的，要是我错了也无所谓，新年快乐。 问题我觉得就出在正数第八行（旧版本知乎翻不到写公式的东西所以纯文字了） “若对于任意一个n属于正整数，使得2n均属于'A，则-1不是质数” 然后我们翻看此前的定义“…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_det